dct_title_s: 1925 First National touring map : state map of main highways and lakes of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights.; Shows state trunk highways and other gravelled and non-gravelled main roads.; Cover title.; "Copyright 1924 by McGill-Warner Co., St. Paul, Minn."; "Compliments of the First National Bank of Saint Paul."; Includes inset map of Minneapolis-Saint Paul and vicinity.; Minnesota trunk highway distance schedule table from the Minnesota Highway Department, St. Paul, Minn., on verso.
